sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend (Browser / Ajax)
    participant API as Backend REST API
    participant DS as Product Detail Service
    participant DB as Database

    U->>FE: Click "Quick View" icon

    FE->>API: GET /api/products/{product_id}

    API->>DS: getProductById(product_id)

    DS->>DB: SELECT * FROM PRODUCTS WHERE product_id=?

    DB-->>DS: product

    DS-->>API: Product

    API-->>FE: ApiResponse<Product>

    FE-->>U: Display product modal